# Task 1: Digital Literacy Awareness Infographic

## Description

The objective of this task is to create a one-page digital infographic that helps students understand the concept of digital literacy and its importance in everyday life. Digital literacy refers to the ability to use technology effectively, safely, and responsibly.

For this task, a visual infographic was designed using a simple and user-friendly tool like Canva. The infographic covers key topics such as useful digital tools for students, safe internet practices, professional online presence, and email etiquette. The content is presented using short points, clear headings, and simple icons to make it easy to understand.

The aim of this infographic is to spread awareness among students about how to use digital platforms properly, stay safe online, and build a positive digital identity. The design focuses on clarity, simplicity, and visual appeal so that the information can be quickly understood by viewers.
